{"tid":1837554,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"大龍就是那古蛇，名叫魔鬼，又叫撒但，是迷惑普天下。","createTime":"2020-01-23T16:31:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-23T17:20:45.000Z","uid":222978,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"59a37c295ad99b0ea76062a4a5b9bdefbb7d8bcd","tid":1837554,"uid":222978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T16:31:20.000Z","msg":"在《啟示錄》的第二十章第一節﹐約翰「又看見一位天使從天降下，手裡拿著無底坑的鑰匙，和一條大鍊子。」第二十章第二節﹐「他捉住那龍，<span style=\"color: red;\">就是古蛇，又叫魔鬼</span>，也叫撒但，把他捆綁一千年」，第二十章第三節﹐「扔在無底坑裡，將無底坑關閉，用印封上，使他不得再迷惑列國，等到那一千年完了。以後必須暫時釋放他。」<br />\n<br />\n【武漢肺炎】內地研究指新病毒疑經<span style=\"color: red;\">蛇</span>傳播 或由<span style=\"color: red;\">蝙蝠</span>與不明病毒重組<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200123/ASPW34QCBEY5OI6UQ7DPO5U4SU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200123%2FASPW34QCBEY5OI6UQ7DPO5U4SU%2F&d=3vKtw9Y9osNHyU2tDi1UeILj0gigvT8yTat38OYNh6E%3D&h=b9368c25\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200123%2FASPW34QCBEY5OI6UQ7DPO5U4SU%2F&h=52139e13\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200123/ASPW34QCBEY5OI6UQ7DPO5U4SU/</a><br />\n<br />\n又是蛇又是蝙蝠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今次真係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">天滅中共<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n有冇黃絲教徒分享下睇法<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6ef780433283a09de0289ed2b886915aaeb9107","tid":1837554,"uid":249979,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T16:43:07.000Z","msg":"共產主義，馬克思，信奉撒旦教，無神論者，消滅一切宗教，奴役全人類。<br />\n所有共產主義國家元首暗地裡都係信奉撒旦教，殘害人類。"},{"pid":"16ea854ebcb1d62dc707a971246ce879b19767fd","tid":1837554,"uid":271130,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T16:45:00.000Z","msg":"根本支那就係撒旦"},{"pid":"c9f39e20f129c7c915e10325cc65fcfb8029305d","tid":1837554,"uid":101307,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"16ea854ebcb1d62dc707a971246ce879b19767fd","tid":1837554,"uid":271130,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T16:45:00.000Z","msg":"根本支那就係撒旦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T16:47:30.000Z","msg":"支那本身冇問題 中共先係問題<br />\n借今次機會拉攏多啲淺藍 等佢地睇清中港共做緊啲乜鳩野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c618b8e5d59a28417c0ac604727902ac76de9cf","tid":1837554,"uid":249979,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T16:49:08.000Z","msg":"馬克思是撒旦教徒，他不是無神論者 ，也不是社會主義者。<br />\n<br />\n在莫斯科的馬克思研究所里有一百多卷馬克思寫的文字，只有十三卷出版了。在這些未出版文字中，表達了馬克思的撒旦魔教徒思想。<span style=\"color: red;\">他仇恨上帝，仇恨上帝的子民人類。馬克思與撒旦簽約毀滅人類。</span>這就不難理解為什麼馬思想和馬主義的信徒如<span style=\"color: red;\">史達林和毛澤東等在掌權後都是暴君和殺人魔王。</span>馬克思青年時代加入撒旦教，成為魔教成員。撒旦教信徒並非無神論者，<span style=\"color: red;\">他們相信神的存在，只是他們仇視神，想超過神，爬在神的上面，至少要和神平起平坐。</span>在《人之傲》（Human Pride）一詩中，<span style=\"color: red;\">馬克思承認，他的目標並不是改善、改組、或革新世界，而是要毀滅世界，並以此為樂。</span>在劇本《Oulanem》中，Oulanem是撒旦的一個宗教儀式名稱，馬克思把自己的靈魂賣給了魔鬼。在馬克思死後不久，他的女傭海倫（Helen Demuth）說，馬克思在病重時獨自在房間裡對著一排點燃的蠟燭祈禱，頭上纏著帶子。其祈禱儀 式不是猶太教的，也不是基督教的，可能是撒旦教的秘密儀式。馬克思死於1883年3月14日，埋在倫敦的高門墓地（Highgate Cemetary），而這個高門墓地是倫敦地區撒旦崇拜的中心，許多崇拜魔鬼的神秘黑色儀式在這個墓地舉行。馬克思在《共產黨宣言》等書中聲稱為無產階級而奮鬥，但是卻稱無產階級的人為「蠢蛋、惡棍、屁股」，稱黑人為「白痴」 ，甚至擁護北美的奴隸制&hellip;&hellip;，在馬克思做德語報紙《Rheinische Zeitung（萊茵報）》的主編時，這本雜誌「不承認當前形式的共產主義理論的有效性，更不用說希望將其付諸實踐？這無論如何都是不可能的&hellip;&hellip;」"},{"pid":"d71334d6bfdb7688d5396847d2af154590c6df1b","tid":1837554,"uid":222978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b6ef780433283a09de0289ed2b886915aaeb9107","tid":1837554,"uid":249979,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T16:43:07.000Z","msg":"共產主義，馬克思，信奉撒旦教，無神論者，消滅一切宗教，奴役全人類。<br />\n所有共產主義國家元首暗地裡都係信奉撒旦教，殘害人類。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T16:50:12.000Z","msg":"也叫撒旦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌真係唔到你唔信<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但上帝可唔可以唔好鎖一千年咁少<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42bf84ec30ced9c4b5ef3e21caa93ce8b8adb8e2","tid":1837554,"uid":249979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d71334d6bfdb7688d5396847d2af154590c6df1b","tid":1837554,"uid":222978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b6ef780433283a09de0289ed2b886915aaeb9107","tid":1837554,"uid":249979,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T16:43:07.000Z","msg":"共產主義，馬克思，信奉撒旦教，無神論者，消滅一切宗教，奴役全人類。<br />\n所有共產主義國家元首暗地裡都係信奉撒旦教，殘害人類。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T16:50:12.000Z","msg":"也叫撒旦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌真係唔到你唔信<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但上帝可唔可以唔好鎖一千年咁少<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T16:52:38.000Z","msg":"21世紀共產主義之首＝中共"},{"pid":"3c3fd8971c59d7d6ded854b455ab8d6c7d650cb1","tid":1837554,"uid":271130,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c9f39e20f129c7c915e10325cc65fcfb8029305d","tid":1837554,"uid":101307,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1